column5: Happy Birthday Pete. We wish you all the best .And hope you have a great day.So sit back and enjoy the day because it's all yours Brother. Dan
Well heck, if I had known that I'd have given you a boot in the backside   Happy Birthday,  Maureen
Hope you had a gerat day buddy,and many many more to ya......Sorry again that our paths didn't cross last week,but there's always November.....TC and tight lines.....Chuck.....
Happy Birthday Peter! I hope you're feeling better from all that sun you got out fishing.
Hey Peter, you have a good day buddy...
